snippet.title: Forward to the Sky Trailer
snippet.description:
Play on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/333250
Game website: http://www.animugame.com

Forward to the Sky is a third person action adventure game in the sky tower ruin, features a mixture of puzzles, action and adventure You are going to collect all the crystal pieces to connect the story and everything will be revealed once Princess reaches the top level.
